        "description": "Retrospective chart and device-log review across three cardiac surgery centres (2019–2023). Hemolysis indices were extracted from post-operative plasma free haemoglobin measurements and normalised to the predicate device RH metric. No experimental manipulation of pump parameters was performed; operating conditions were recorded as-delivered by clinical staff.",
